Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:25.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ベルゼビュート）\Nハッハッハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:29.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッハッハッハ…
Dialogue: 9,0:00:30.76,0:00:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bahamut has finally reawakened!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:34.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バハムートの復活は\N成し遂げられた
Dialogue: 9,0:00:34.77,0:00:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Heed my words, gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:35.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神々よ
Dialogue: 9,0:00:36.10,0:00:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Our long-standing war has now come to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:41.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,永きにわたる戦いに\Nこれで終止符が打たれる
Dialogue: 9,0:00:42.11,0:00:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You will now prostrate before us demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:46.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我ら悪魔の前に\Nひれ伏すがよい
Dialogue: 9,0:00:46.61,0:00:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Heed my words as well, all of demonkind!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.73,0:00:50.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして\N全ての魔の者たちよ
Dialogue: 9,0:00:50.89,0:00:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Etch my name into your memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:54.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が名を\Nその胸に刻むがよい
Dialogue: 9,0:00:54.74,0:01:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Beelzebub! At the top I stand, above all others!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.87,0:01:00.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全ての頂点に立つ者\Nベルゼビュートの名を！
Dialogue: 9,0:01:06.99,0:01:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, demonstrate your almighty power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:08.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ベルゼビュート）\Nさあ 見せてみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:11.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の力
Dialogue: 9,0:01:28.99,0:01:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:30.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜだ…
Dialogue: 9,0:01:44.23,0:01:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:46.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ラヴァレイ）\Nすばらしい…
Dialogue: 9,0:01:53.31,0:01:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, Captain Lavalley? Why you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:55.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カイザル）\Nなぜだ ラヴァレイ隊長…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:56.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ あなたが！
Dialogue: 9,0:01:56.60,0:01:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the one behind everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:58.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リタ）\Nあいつが全ての元凶よ
Dialogue: 9,0:01:59.43,0:02:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys ending up in Helheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:01.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたたちが\Nヘルヘイムに行ってしまったのも
Dialogue: 9,0:02:01.98,0:02:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeanne turning into a demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:03.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンヌが悪魔になったのも
Dialogue: 9,0:02:03.99,0:02:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all part of his deception!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全て この男が仕組んだうそ
Dialogue: 9,0:02:07.23,0:02:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:08.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけじゃない
Dialogue: 9,0:02:08.69,0:02:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This man manipulated everyone—gods, demons, {\i1}and{\i0} humans—into reviving Bahamut.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:12.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この男は神も悪魔も人間も\N全部だまして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:14.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バハムートを復活させたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:17.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ラヴァレイ）\Nフフ… なかなか理解がよろしい
Dialogue: 9,0:02:15.35,0:02:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very perceptive, I must say.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:41.41,0:02:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over, woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（オス犬）\Nもうダメワン
Dialogue: 9,0:02:42.70,0:02:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're dead meat, woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:44.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（メス犬）\N死ぬしかないワン
Dialogue: 9,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケルベロス）\Nそんなのやだあ～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:49.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひえ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:02.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ… ラヴァレイ
Dialogue: 9,0:03:01.30,0:03:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Lavalley...
Dialogue: 9,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who exactly are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様 一体 何者だ！
Dialogue: 9,0:03:04.94,0:03:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,His real name is Gilles de Rais.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:06.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつの名はジルドレイ
Dialogue: 9,0:03:07.33,0:03:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A man with a bounty on his head who's taken countless lives with his gruesome sorcery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:08.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪趣味な魔術で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:12.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これまでに数えきれないほどの命を\N奪ってきた賞金首
Dialogue: 9,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A bounty?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,賞金首？
Dialogue: 9,0:03:14.24,0:03:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. This is all according to Bacchus, but he seems pretty certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:18.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リタ）\Nええ バッカスの情報だけど\N間違いなさそうね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:19.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カイザル）\Nこんなもの！
Dialogue: 9,0:03:18.27,0:03:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have this back!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:22.78,0:03:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you two please keep it down for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:26.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君たち\N少し静かにしてもらえないか？
Dialogue: 9,0:03:28.05,0:03:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to fully savor the moment the world ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:33.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界が終わる この瞬間を\N味わい尽くしておきたいからな
Dialogue: 9,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You wretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様！
Dialogue: 9,0:03:40.03,0:03:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you not hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ジルドレイ）\N聞こえなかったかな？
Dialogue: 9,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,離れなさい！
Dialogue: 9,0:03:47.58,0:03:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I kindly asked you to keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,静かにしろと\N言ってるじゃないですか
Dialogue: 9,0:03:50.78,0:03:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight's blade cuts very well, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:54.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,にしても 今宵(こよい)の刃(やいば)は よく斬れる
Dialogue: 9,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,His face...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:55.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その顔…
Dialogue: 9,0:04:01.73,0:04:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A momentous, once-in-a-lifetime event is\Nunfolding before our very eyes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:07.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（マルチネ）\N一度きりの大事なイベントが\N今 目の前で行われているのですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:09.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カイザル）\Nぐう…
Dialogue: 9,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the world's destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（マルチネ）\N世界の破滅！
Dialogue: 9,0:04:14.80,0:04:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you simply enjoy this marvelous event?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:17.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ このすばらしいときを\N楽しめないのですか？
Dialogue: 9,0:04:17.99,0:04:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:19.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はな… せ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:26.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ジルドレイ:カイザルの声で）\Nああ… 体が安定していないな
Dialogue: 9,0:04:24.31,0:04:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My body seems a bit unstable.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:28.72,0:04:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:29.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失礼
Dialogue: 9,0:04:29.95,0:04:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you took too many of those iffy concoctions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:33.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと\Nヤバい薬の飲み過ぎじゃないかしら
Dialogue: 9,0:04:33.74,0:04:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we're both stuck in unfortunate bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:36.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お互い不憫(ふびん)な体だな
Dialogue: 9,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite the relentless one, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ジルドレイ）\N君は どうにも落ち着きがないな
Dialogue: 9,0:04:49.66,0:04:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to run amok that badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなに暴れたければ…
Dialogue: 9,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,then do so with your old friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:54.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親友に相手をしてもらいたまえ
Dialogue: 9,0:05:06.07,0:05:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what? I'm all out of antidotes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:08.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう解毒薬ないんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:43.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が魔力より生まれし アーミラ
Dialogue: 9,0:05:39.35,0:05:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Amira was born of my power and served as the key for Bahamut's awakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:46.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを依代(よりしろ)とした復活…
Dialogue: 9,0:05:46.87,0:05:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I unable to control him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:50.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ バハムートを操れぬ
Dialogue: 9,0:05:50.93,0:05:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Curse you, Martinet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:53.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おのれ マルチ…
Dialogue: 9,0:05:58.87,0:06:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've paid you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アザゼル）\N借りは返したぞ
Dialogue: 9,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're even now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:05.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借りは返したが…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（シャリオス）\Nし… 死にたくない
Dialogue: 9,0:06:30.87,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die! I don't want to die yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:33.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ死にたく…
Dialogue: 9,0:06:35.28,0:06:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother! Please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,母上！　お助けください！
Dialogue: 9,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:40.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,母上～！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カイザル）\Nええい！
Dialogue: 9,0:07:04.16,0:07:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rita! I'm going to settle things with Favaro once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リタ！\Nファバロとは ここで決着をつける
Dialogue: 9,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手を出さないでくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:14.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた…
Dialogue: 9,0:07:13.98,0:07:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not the time to be acting like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:17.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと\N言ってる場合じゃないでしょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:38.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リタ）\Nひゃあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:41.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きゃあ！
Dialogue: 9,0:08:14.38,0:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaisar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:15.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイザル！
Dialogue: 9,0:08:39.78,0:08:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That was very entertaining, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:42.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なかなか面白い余興だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:46.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ファバロ）\N１つ忠告しておく
Dialogue: 9,0:08:44.64,0:08:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I got some advice for you.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:48.52,0:08:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got a bounty on your head, you oughta be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:53.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も賞金首なら\Nもっと警戒心を持つべきだ
Dialogue: 9,0:08:53.36,0:08:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of things like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:54.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,例えば…
Dialogue: 9,0:08:55.47,0:08:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Seel Soh... Cetom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:58.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シール･ソー･ケトム！
Dialogue: 9,0:09:17.97,0:09:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...knights that still got their old bounty hunter wristbands!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:20.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,元賞金稼ぎの騎士が\Nつける
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この腕輪とかにな！
Dialogue: 9,0:09:31.36,0:09:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. When exactly did you turn back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:34.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リタ）\Nあんた いつから元に戻ってたの？
Dialogue: 9,0:09:34.83,0:09:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since Kaisar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:35.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ファバロ）\Nカイザルに…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっつい一発を\N撃ち込まれたときからだ
Dialogue: 9,0:09:38.07,0:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,gave me his harsh wake-up call.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:40.80,0:09:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,His what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なによ それ？
Dialogue: 9,0:09:42.43,0:09:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I affixed an antidote to the end of my crossbow arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:45.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボウガンの矢の先に\N仕込んでおいたのだ
Dialogue: 9,0:09:46.01,0:09:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to catch the one you dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:48.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リタが落とした解毒薬を拾ってな
Dialogue: 9,0:09:49.22,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaisar and I threw together a little act so no one would notice afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:52.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは バレねえように\Nカイザルと口裏合わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いっちょ上がりだ
Dialogue: 9,0:09:54.27,0:09:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Never thought I'd lop off your arm, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:57.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがに腕を斬ることになるとは\N思わなかったが
Dialogue: 9,0:09:57.44,0:10:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That nefarious liar wouldn't have been fooled otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:10:00.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カイザル）\Nあの大うそつきをだますには\Nそれくらい必要だ
Dialogue: 9,0:10:00.63,0:10:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Still though, letting your arm get chopped off...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからって\Nホントに腕を斬っちゃうなんて
Dialogue: 9,0:10:03.70,0:10:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:05.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リタ）バカよ\N（カイザル）ぐぐぐ…
Dialogue: 9,0:10:05.51,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:06.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（バッカス）\Nよくやったな
Dialogue: 9,0:10:08.06,0:10:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, you look totally beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:10.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ファバロ）\Nおお 派手にやられたな
Dialogue: 9,0:10:10.50,0:10:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all thanks to that lunatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:13.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（バッカス）\Nああ そのイカレ野郎のせいでな
Dialogue: 9,0:10:13.35,0:10:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can expect a handsome reward, I hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,報酬は弾んでくれるんだろ？
Dialogue: 9,0:10:15.63,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. More than you could possibly spend in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:20.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その日のうちには\N使いきれねえくらいにな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:22.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつは楽しみだ
Dialogue: 9,0:10:20.56,0:10:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:22.64,0:10:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:23.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど…
Dialogue: 9,0:10:26.05,0:10:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll be hitting the pubs anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:28.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ飲みには\N行けそうにねえな
Dialogue: 9,0:10:28.86,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Lady Amira?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カイザル）\Nアーミラ嬢か？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:31.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ファバロ）\Nこれは俺が
Dialogue: 9,0:10:30.63,0:10:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'll have to finish this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:33.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けりをつけなきゃ\Nならないみたいだからな
Dialogue: 9,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've made up your mind, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:36.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腹を決めたってわけだな？
Dialogue: 9,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も協力しよう
Dialogue: 9,0:10:41.30,0:10:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Get real. You know you're in no condition to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:44.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リタ）\Nあんた\Nそのけがで行けるわけないでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:45.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ファバロ）\Nカイザル
Dialogue: 9,0:10:44.78,0:10:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaisar.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill Amira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:49.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はアーミラを殺す
Dialogue: 9,0:10:50.57,0:10:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. This is no time for such levity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:53.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前\Nこんなときに 何を冗談言って…
Dialogue: 9,0:10:56.92,0:11:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an inexcusable thing to say, even as a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:11:00.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たとえ冗談でも\N許される言葉ではないぞ！
Dialogue: 9,0:11:00.32,0:11:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Once someone has become one\Nwith Bahamut, they can never be separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:04.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バハムートとひとつになった者を\N切り離すことは 二度とできない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:07.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツを止めるには\Nアーミラを殺すしかないんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:11:04.84,0:11:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing Amira is the only way to stop that thing now.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:07.64,0:11:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be some other way! Have you thought of one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:10.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か方法くらいあるだろ？\N探したのか？
Dialogue: 9,0:11:11.93,0:11:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other way. The old\Ndragon in the forest told me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:14.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ファバロ）\N森にいたドラゴンのじいさんから\N言われていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:16.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかに方法はない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:27.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カイザル）\Nそんな…
Dialogue: 9,0:11:26.42,0:11:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 9,0:11:27.60,0:11:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I swore that I would save Lady Amira without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は必ず\Nアーミラ嬢を救い出すと誓ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前には殺させない
Dialogue: 9,0:11:31.97,0:11:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you kill her!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:33.75,0:11:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}will{\i0} bring her back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が必ず 生きて連れ戻してみせる
Dialogue: 9,0:11:41.54,0:11:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaisar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ファバロ）\Nなあ カイザル
Dialogue: 9,0:11:43.43,0:11:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want her to suffer any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:46.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう これ以上\Nあいつを悲しませたくないんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:11:46.87,0:11:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to end this for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:48.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちの手で止めてやろうぜ
Dialogue: 9,0:11:50.30,0:11:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bacchus, I wanna get up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バッカス あそこに行きたいんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Any ideas how?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:55.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か方法はないかな？
Dialogue: 9,0:11:56.54,0:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:58.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しょうがねえな
Dialogue: 9,0:11:58.36,0:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hansa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（バッカス）ハンサ\N（ハンサ）はい？
Dialogue: 9,0:11:59.15,0:11:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:59.69,0:12:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry him there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が運んでやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:02.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（バッカス）はい～！\N（ハンサ）くわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ハンサ）\Nくわ～
Dialogue: 9,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カイザル）\N待て 私も行く
Dialogue: 9,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Changed your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:13.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気が変わったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違う！
Dialogue: 9,0:12:13.65,0:12:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:14.78,0:12:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to release Lady Amira from Bahamut's spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:17.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アーミラ嬢をバハムートの呪縛から\N解き放つためだ！
Dialogue: 9,0:12:24.59,0:12:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Be back in a jiffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:27.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんじゃ ちょいと行ってくるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ハンサ）く～わ！\N（カイザル･ファバロ）ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:35.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ハンサ）\Nくわっ くわっ くわっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ハンサ）くわ～！\N（２人）うわあああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:06.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメです！　近づけません
Dialogue: 9,0:13:04.20,0:13:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use! I can't get any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,諦めるな　行け！
Dialogue: 9,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up! Keep going!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:18.14,0:13:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:20.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くわっ！　くわっ… あっつ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:23.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ…\Nせめて 少しの間 動きが止まれば
Dialogue: 9,0:13:20.94,0:13:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If only he'd stay still for a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:24.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは…
Dialogue: 9,0:13:24.17,0:13:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ファバロ）\N行けるぞ！
Dialogue: 9,0:14:53.98,0:14:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ファバロ）\Nおっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お～らあ！
Dialogue: 9,0:15:59.40,0:16:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Favaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:00.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい！　ファバロ！
Dialogue: 9,0:16:09.22,0:16:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:10.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前…
Dialogue: 9,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Amira!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アーミラ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:55.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聖なる… 騎士
Dialogue: 9,0:16:53.37,0:16:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy Knight...
Dialogue: 9,0:17:02.07,0:17:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Favaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ファバロ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ファバロ）\Nおわっ！
Dialogue: 9,0:17:13.26,0:17:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't look at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んな にらむなって…
Dialogue: 9,0:17:27.63,0:17:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Amira...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:28.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ファバロ）\Nアーミラ…
Dialogue: 9,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally came!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:30.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アーミラ）\Nやっと来た
Dialogue: 9,0:17:30.03,0:17:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I still need you to get this damn tail off of me, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:35.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この いまいましい尻尾\Nまだ取ってもらってないからな
Dialogue: 9,0:17:39.07,0:17:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding! Forget I said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:41.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,がっ… うそ！　今のは なし！
Dialogue: 9,0:17:41.24,0:17:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Amira! Whenever you're\Nin trouble, I'll rush to your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:44.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アーミラ\Nお前のピンチには いつだって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は駆けつける
Dialogue: 9,0:17:46.37,0:17:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Always have and always will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:47.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これまでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:49.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これからもな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:50.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アーミラ）\Nうそ
Dialogue: 9,0:17:50.27,0:17:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ファバロ）\Nうそじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 9,0:17:53.18,0:17:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about your mom, though. We couldn't save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:56.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど お前の母ちゃんは悪かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:57.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けられなくて
Dialogue: 9,0:17:57.69,0:17:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:58.96,0:18:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She really did recognize me when I hugged her then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのとき…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:04.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,抱き締めた あのとき\Nお母さん 分かってくれた
Dialogue: 9,0:18:06.76,0:18:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:07.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジか？
Dialogue: 9,0:18:08.56,0:18:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you said, Fava!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:09.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ファバの言うとおり
Dialogue: 9,0:18:09.91,0:18:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘッ… まあな
Dialogue: 9,0:18:12.78,0:18:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Amira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:14.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ アーミラ
Dialogue: 9,0:18:14.25,0:18:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I'm gonna take you to a {\i1}much{\i0} better place than lousy ol' Helheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:15.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度はヘルヘイムなんかより
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:18.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと面白(おもしれ)えとこに\N連れてってやるからな
Dialogue: 9,0:18:22.07,0:18:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's all sorts of stuff I wanna show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:25.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前に見せてやりたいもんが\Nいっぱいあるからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:26.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うそ
Dialogue: 9,0:18:26.04,0:18:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うそじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 9,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:30.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら 俺の目を見ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふん！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:03.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう ファバロ…
Dialogue: 9,0:19:00.94,0:19:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Favaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか… ヤバくない？
Dialogue: 9,0:19:24.89,0:19:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just me or does this look bad?
Dialogue: 9,0:19:32.82,0:19:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Get on quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ハンサ）\N早く！　早く乗ってください
Dialogue: 9,0:19:35.41,0:19:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But Favaro isn't back yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:37.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カイザル）\Nだが まだファバロが！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:43.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:44.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くわあああ！
Dialogue: 9,0:20:16.81,0:20:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Favaro!
