Dialogue: 9,0:20:38.59,0:20:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Captain Kaisar! It's time to address the troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（団長騎士）\N騎士カイザル
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,副官として号令を
Dialogue: 9,0:20:47.78,0:20:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today marks the coronation of the new king!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:50.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（団長騎士）\N本日は新たな王の即位式である！
Dialogue: 9,0:20:50.85,0:20:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We, the Orléans Knights, are tasked...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これより オルレアン騎士団は…
Dialogue: 9,0:20:52.41,0:20:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Captain Kaisar here yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ジャンヌ）\Nカイザル隊長は まだか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:01.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（店主）\Nバハムートに\N世界が滅ぼされそうになったとき
Dialogue: 9,0:20:58.74,0:21:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when Bahamut was about to destroy our world,
Dialogue: 9,0:21:02.10,0:21:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the knight of legend appeared and\Nbanished him to another world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伝説の騎士が現れて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:06.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっか違う世界に\N追っ払ったんだろ？
Dialogue: 9,0:21:06.79,0:21:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he's dead now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:08.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしかして 死んじまったのかな？
Dialogue: 9,0:21:11.14,0:21:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ファバロ）\Nいや…
Dialogue: 9,0:21:12.90,0:21:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bahamut will never, ever die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:15.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バハムートは死んだりしねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:16.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,永遠に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:21.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと またいつか 現れるだろうよ
Dialogue: 9,0:21:18.35,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll show up again someday.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きてるよ…
Dialogue: 9,0:21:35.43,0:21:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way is the wind blowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:38.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,風は どっちに吹いている？
Dialogue: 9,0:21:38.61,0:21:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:40.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明日だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:41.06,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}People always say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.06,0:21:44.65,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}"black or white," but the world is so gray
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:49.90,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Even angels and demons were once the son of God I praised
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:53.99,OP_Romaji_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}temee no gen'in wa temee no naka kara
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:53.99,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You're the catalyst for your own demise
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:56.20,OP_Romaji_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}zenbu hikurumete omae no saga
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:56.20,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}It's inherent to your being
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:21:59.08,OP_Romaji_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}kizuku koro ni wa mou you're in a coffin
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:21:59.08,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}But by the time you realize, you're in a coffin
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:01.58,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}It's too late if you want to do something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:04.08,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}What the hell is wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.08,0:22:06.96,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I can't remember what I wanted to be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:09.09,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Tick, tack, which is what I found
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.68,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I can see the keys are scattered around
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:16.85,OP_Romaji_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}kono yoru ga aketemo nanika kawaru wake ja nee sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:16.85,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Even though a new day dawns, nothing's gonna change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:21.89,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Yes, I know; yes, I know that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.81,0:22:24.40,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'm the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:27.48,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}who can save myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:30.82,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll never forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:35.07,OP_English_12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}All I wanna be is me
